com.github.lwhite1.tablesaw.columns

Interface Column

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BooleanMapUtils, CategoryColumnUtils, CategoryFilters, CategoryReduceUtils, DateColumnUtils, DateMapUtils, DateTImeColumnUtils, DateTimeMapUtils, FloatColumnUtils, IntColumnUtils, IntMapUtils, LongColumnUtils, LongMapUtils, ShortColumnUtils, ShortMapUtils, TimeColumnUtils, TimeMapUtils
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractColumn, BooleanColumn, CategoryColumn, DateColumn, DateTimeColumn, FloatColumn, IntColumn, LongColumn, ShortColumn, TimeColumn, TimeIntervalColumn

    public interface Column
    The general interface for columns.

    Columns can either exist on their own or be a part of a table. All the data in a single column is of a particular type.
